273
00:12:20,500 --> 00:12:22,340
But ask yourself

274
00:12:23,020 --> 00:12:24,020
how well

275
00:12:24,020 --> 00:12:25,580
you know her.

276
00:12:26,140 --> 00:12:27,340
You're familiar

277
00:12:27,340 --> 00:12:28,260
